body:
The code below sets bit 3 of all members of array a.  I should print '8888' (tested with vcs).
However, I got this error running with "iverilog -g2012"

> mda.v:8: error: A reference to a wire or reg (`i') is not allowed in a constant expression.
> mda.v:8: error: Array index expressions must be constant here.

```systemverilog
module test;

  logic [3:0][3:0] a;

  initial begin
    a = 0;
    for (int i=0; i<4; i++)
      a[i][3] = 1;
    $display("%h", a);
    $finish;
  end

endmodule
```

